Context: {context}
Question: {question}
Instructions: 1. Answer the question using ONLY information from the context above 2. If the context doesn't contain enough information, say "I don't have enough information to answer this question" 3. Cite the source for each piece of information using [Source: filename] 4. Be concise but complete in your answer
Answer: """
